09:50.215 --> 09:52.217
Sure.

10:03.020 --> 10:05.230
You know, this drought's
been going on for three years.

10:05.272 --> 10:09.234
- Look at this. Never know it.
- Yeah.

10:09.276 --> 10:12.154
Green, green, green,
green, green.

10:12.195 --> 10:14.406
- It's unbelievable.
- What's this field over here?

10:14.448 --> 10:16.366
That's citrus. Oranges,

10:16.408 --> 10:19.202
