offered to buy my land.

11:10.170 --> 11:13.256
BILLY: Really?
Was it before or after it collapsed?

11:13.298 --> 11:15.133
- GENE: After.
- Oh.

11:15.175 --> 11:17.135
BILLY: You still have
that note he sent you?

11:17.177 --> 11:19.179
GENE: Yeah, somewhere.

11:19.221 --> 11:23.058
BILLY: You may want to hang on to it.
