for no reason.

13:01.656 --> 13:03.200
Oh, oh, is that Billy?

13:03.241 --> 13:04.326
- No, it's not.
- Hi, Billy!

13:04.367 --> 13:06.036
When you coming home?

13:06.077 --> 13:09.372
- She got to go.
- I'm-I'm not kicking her out,

13:09.414 --> 13:11.082
- I told you that.
- I will kick her out.

13:11.124 --> 13:13.460
- I will kick her out.
- She'll grow on you,

13:13.502 --> 13:15.045
trust me.
