13:23.136 --> 13:25.514
- How you doing?
- Oh, I'm okay.

13:25.555 --> 13:26.932
How's Gene?

13:26.973 --> 13:30.018
- Not good, of course.
- Aw, poor guy.

13:30.060 --> 13:32.812
