president of the water board,

17:01.646 --> 17:03.440
- right?
- Correct.

17:03.481 --> 17:05.316
How does that work, you know?

17:05.358 --> 17:07.318
I'd like to talk to him.

17:07.359 --> 17:09.194
You'll need to make
an appointment.

17:09.237 --> 17:11.321
Excellent.
Let's make an appointment.

17:11.364 --> 17:12.615
- I'm out to lunch.
- Well, I mean, not yet.

17:12.656 --> 17:15.242
We could make, you can make
an appointment, right?

17:15.285 --> 17:18.037
- It'll only take a second.
- If you need more information,

17:18.079 --> 17:22.459
this video on the history
of the California Aqueduct...

17:23.501 --> 17:25.920
...is very informative.

17:29.382 --> 17:32.177
- (QUIETLY): Sorry about that.
- Mm.

17:32.218 --> 17:35.263
