the basis of all life.

17:35.305 --> 17:37.807
It's eternal,
and it's old as time.

17:37.849 --> 17:39.726
- (DOOR CHIMES)
- The same molecules

17:39.768 --> 17:41.770
in your drinking water
once flowed

17:41.811 --> 17:43.313
through the bodies of dinosaurs.

17:43.354 --> 17:46.524
But in California,
more than two-thirds

17:46.566 --> 17:49.861
of the state's freshwater
is only found

17:49.903 --> 17:53.239
in the northernmost region,
far from the dense city centers

17:53.281 --> 17:55.867
of the arid south as well
as the nutrient-rich soil

17:55.909 --> 17:57.869
of the barren Central Valley.

