24:18.541 --> 24:20.251
That's 'cause you're not
trying hard enough.

24:20.293 --> 24:21.878
- (CHUCKLES) I don't know.
- (CHUCKLES)

24:21.919 --> 24:24.338
Uh, I'm a hell of a lot better
drinker than I am a gambler.

24:24.380 --> 24:26.424
Well, we got that, too,
