28:36.173 --> 28:39.051
- (AUDIENCE APPLAUDING)
- I've never been here before.

28:41.095 --> 28:43.931
Well, my mistake, then.

28:43.973 --> 28:45.516
Jimmy.

28:45.558 --> 28:48.227
Mr. McBride's tab
is on the house tonight.

28:48.269 --> 28:52.356
And, uh, get Mr. Blackwood's
address for him in Encino.

28:52.398 --> 28:54.275
(TAPS BAR)

28:54.316 --> 28:56.277
Appreciate it.

28:56.318 --> 28:59.613
Oh, and, uh...
enjoy your evening.

28:59.655 --> 29:01.740
Thank you, sir.

29:01.782 --> 29:03.534
