29:03.576 --> 29:05.578
Excuse me.

29:05.619 --> 29:07.288
- Me?
- Can I ask you a question?

29:07.329 --> 29:10.082
Sure, why not?

29:10.124 --> 29:12.126
Do you believe
in love at first sight?

29:12.168 --> 29:14.128
(CHUCKLES)

29:14.170 --> 29:16.755
Um...

29:17.923 --> 29:19.884
Yeah, actually, I do.

29:19.925 --> 29:22.470
- Me, too.
- Yeah, good deal.

29:22.511 --> 29:25.055
- (CHUCKLES)
- How have you been?

29:27.683 --> 29:29.643
Been all right. You?

29:29.685 --> 29:32.897
Good. Real good.

29:39.236 --> 29:41.238
(COINS CLINKING)

29:50.581 --> 29:53.667
He, uh, says he doesn't remember

29:53.709 --> 29:55.711
- being here.
- Hmm.

29:57.713 --> 30:00.799
Let's keep an eye
on that campfire.

30:00.841 --> 30:03.594
I don't want it
getting out of control.

30:03.636 --> 30:05.596
Got it.

30:05.638 --> 30:07.556
(ELEVATOR DOORS OPEN)

30:14.438 --> 30:15.773
(BEEPS)

30:17.775 --> 30:20.027
MAN: McBride's downstairs.

30:20.069 --> 30:22.071
(SOFT CHATTER CONTINUES)

30:23.656 --> 30:26.075
MAN: Unimpressive dude.

30:26.116 --> 30:29.828
- Don't underestimate him.
- Well, he doesn't know much.

30:29.870 --> 30:31.830
What is he gonna find out?

30:31.872 --> 30:34.208
- Totally agree.
- MAN 2: What do you mean?

30:34.250 --> 30:37.002
- I mean, there's...
- You two, just listen.

30:37.044 --> 30:40.297
Wade, it was his wife.

30:40.339 --> 30:41.924
