30:41.966 --> 30:43.676
BLACKWOOD: You're probably right.

30:43.717 --> 30:45.553
But let's not worry

30:45.594 --> 30:47.429
just for worry's sake.

30:47.471 --> 30:50.558
Have you ever known me to worry
for no good reason?

30:51.600 --> 30:52.851
Good.

30:52.893 --> 30:54.728
I'm worried.

30:54.770 --> 30:58.232
I hear you, all right?

30:58.274 --> 31:02.444
But I know
the solution will find us.

31:02.486 --> 31:03.904
It always does.

31:03.946 --> 31:06.365
Oh, put your pom-poms away.

31:06.407 --> 31:09.118
You're gonna lose your spot
