31:09.159 --> 31:11.120
Wha... (CHUCKLES)

31:11.161 --> 31:13.956
You comfortable here?

31:13.998 --> 31:16.750
- Yes, sir.
- Yeah? Your family's good?

31:16.792 --> 31:18.419
- Yeah. Yes, sir, they're very well.
- All right.

31:18.460 --> 31:19.753
- All right, then.
- Thank you.

31:19.795 --> 31:21.797
Mm.

