It was horrible.

36:08.917 --> 36:10.419
My condo was destroyed.

36:10.460 --> 36:12.754
I lost my cat.

36:12.796 --> 36:15.924
Anyway, this place...
I know every exit here,

36:15.966 --> 36:17.968
even the secret one,
back by the bathroom,

36:18.010 --> 36:19.303
the one that nobody talks about.

36:19.344 --> 36:21.388
So, if you ever get stuck
back there,

36:21.430 --> 36:23.140
let me know,
I'll show you where it is.

36:23.181 --> 36:27.477
- Yeah, I'll do that.
- Compliments of Mr. Blackwood.

36:27.519 --> 36:29.104
Oh, that's okay. I'm good.

36:29.146 --> 36:33.400
No, Mr. Blackwood knows how long
it takes to drive back to L.A.

36:33.442 --> 36:34.776
But, uh...

36:36.987 --> 36:39.072
...we'll leave it up to you.

36:39.114 --> 36:41.992
Yeah, I appreciate that.

36:42.034 --> 36:44.703
Hey, if you're not
gonna use that, I will.

36:44.745 --> 36:46.788
- What?
- I'm not talking too much, am I?

36:46.830 --> 36:48.415
No. Gosh, no, no.

36:48.457 --> 36:51.919
RITA: Just, my last boyfriend
said I talk too much, so...

36:51.960 --> 36:54.212
He's dead now.

36:54.254 --> 36:56.173
Died in that earthquake.

36:56.214 --> 36:59.176
Along with the cat.

